---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'Is this a religious thing?',
    answer: 'Grove is run by Christians, and our faith shapes why we care about mentoring students. But we\'re not here to preach at you or make anything weird. We lead with genuine value—good projects, real mentorship, actual community. Relationships form naturally over time. No pressure, no awkward conversations, no strings attached.'
  },
  {
    question: 'What if I don\'t want to code?',
    answer: 'That\'s totally fine! We have two tracks that don\'t require any coding. Career Mentorship gives you 1:1 help with resumes, interviews, and career planning. The Transfer Support Network connects transfer students with peers at 4-year universities. Coding is one great option, but it\'s not the only path at Grove.'
  },
  {
    question: 'What\'s the Transfer Support Network?',
    answer: 'It\'s a track specifically for transfer students. We connect you with students from our network of 1,600+ people at 4-year universities who can share their experiences, offer campus insights, and help you navigate the transition. Whether you\'re preparing to transfer or just landed at a new school, we\'ve got people who get it.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Do I need experience to join the Coding track?',
    answer: 'Not much. If you can write a basic function and use git, you\'re ready. Our projects have issues tagged by difficulty level, and mentors are here to help you level up. That said, this isn\'t a "learn to code from scratch" program—we expect you to be learning that through school or on your own. We\'re here to give you real-world practice.'
  },
  {
    question: 'What\'s the time commitment?',
    answer: 'Totally flexible across all tracks. Some folks contribute code a few hours a week, others connect with their mentor occasionally. There are no minimums or deadlines. This is async-friendly and designed to work around your class schedule. The more you put in, the more you\'ll get out—but even small engagement adds up over time.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Is this actually free?',
    answer: 'Yes, 100%. No fees, no hidden costs, no catch. The projects we work on serve real communities, and the mentorship comes from professionals who genuinely want to help. We\'re not a company making money off student labor. We\'re people who want to help the next generation succeed.'
  },
  {
    question: 'What if I\'m not a CS major?',
    answer: 'You\'re welcome here regardless of your major. If you want career mentorship or transfer support, your major doesn\'t matter at all. For the coding track, what matters is curiosity and follow-through—some of the best developers we know came from non-traditional paths.'
  }
];
---

<section id="faq" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-warm-50">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">
        Frequently asked questions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-warm-600">
        Straight answers to the things people actually wonder about.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ List -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      {faqs.map((faq, index) => (
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-warm-200 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 text-left">{faq.question}</h3>
            <svg 
              class="w-5 h-5 text-warm-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" 
              fill="none" 
              stroke="currentColor" 
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">{faq.answer}</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- More questions -->
    <p class="text-center mt-12 text-warm-500">
      Got more questions? <a href="https://forms.example.com/grove-interest" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-grove-600 hover:underline">Fill out the interest form</a>—we'd love to hear from you.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
